{"tid":259900,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"車路士球迷入場告訴熱刺誰是英超冠軍","createTime":"2017-05-27T10:05:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-01T12:45:39.000Z","uid":49279,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a43e93866f97aeed0cb1355361cfca5f6c9ff5ff","tid":259900,"uid":49279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T10:05:19.000Z","msg":"要數倫敦死敵，當然還有今屆一直將熱刺壓在身後的車路士。藍戰士的球衣在大球場特別顯眼，阿言指今季一直提心吊膽害怕被熱刺追上，但今場不撐熱刺不撐傑志，「入場是撐車路士，告訴熱刺誰是英超冠軍」<br />\n<br />\n藍戰士並不獨行，阿言透露在路上看見很多車路士球迷，說罷隨即有三名藍軍球迷路過。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/604160/xlarge/c0b47101490cc535ed4dc5e006e2d80a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F604160%2Fxlarge%2Fc0b47101490cc535ed4dc5e006e2d80a.jpg&h=005a67fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/604170/xlarge/b086409a71538f787344188ea70d73a9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F604170%2Fxlarge%2Fb086409a71538f787344188ea70d73a9.jpg&h=bd245be9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/604171/xlarge/b99a8b8edefb0241c193bd22c826681a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F604171%2Fxlarge%2Fb99a8b8edefb0241c193bd22c826681a.jpg&h=709fe10b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"838b0e5b78295bc875f73a44a47d43570deb4f70","tid":259900,"uid":28155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T10:06:59.000Z","msg":"+2gc <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a30b3cbb3d49f4d79c342aa5ea59ce4852629e42","tid":259900,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T10:07:51.000Z","msg":"放過我轟ok?<br />\n<br />\n個班係t9迷時期轟迷來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{